e where to look?\u003c/p\u003e\\n  \\t\\t\u003cp\u003eSubscribe to The Kyiv Independent’s newsletter, Ukraine Daily.\u003c/p\u003e\\n  \\t\\t\u003cp\u003eWe select the most important war updates, interviews, and explainers, then send them over as a daily update.\u003c/p\u003e\\n  \\t\",\"shortDescription\":\"The latest news and stories from Ukraine, seven days a week\",\"tags\":[\"UD-landing\",\"Ukraine Daily Newsletter\",\"UD-newsletter-page\"],\"newslettersPageTags\":[\"UD-newsletter-page\",\"Ukraine Daily Newsletter\"],\"newsletterLandingTags\":[\"UD-landing\",\"Ukraine Daily Newsletter\"],\"newslettersBoxTags\":[\"UD-newsletters-block\",\"Ukraine Daily Newsletter\"],\"newslettersAccountTags\":[\"UD-account-pref\",\"Ukraine Daily Newsletter\"],\"index\":1,\"mainImgSrc\":\"/assets/images/kiv3/newsletters/newsletter-ukraine-daily-img.png\",\"mainImgObjectPosition\":\"center\",\"imgSrc\":\"/assets/images/kiv3/newsletters/newsletter-ukraine-daily.webp\",\"isMain\":true,\"isDefaultSelected\":true,\"ga\":\"ud\",\"forBox\":true,\"forSignUp\":true}},{\"id\":\"41a7c2de77\",\"name\":\"Ukraine Weekly\",\"extraData\":{\"id\":\"41a7c2de77\",\"href\":\"https://us20.campaign-archive.com/?u=5ede1a4645edfb08941f4a9f9\u0026id=95d43e0fe9\",\"previewHref\":\"https://us20.campaign-archive.com/?u=5ede1a4645edfb08941f4a9f9\u0026id=c2ce12f069\",\"link\":\"ukraine-weekly\",\"name\":\"Ukraine Weekly\",\"description\":\"\\n\\t\\t\\t\u003cp\u003eTo stay up to date with what is happening in Ukraine, sign up for the Kyiv Independent's new newsletter – Ukraine Weekly.\u003c/p\u003e\\n\\t\\t\\t\u003cp\u003eEvery Saturday, the Kyiv Independent's editor-in-chief Olga Rudenko will offer her reflections on key events that shaped the week in Ukraine – and share the best of the Kyiv Independent's journalism.\u003c/p\u003e\\n\\t\\t\",\"shortDescription\":\"Editor-in-Chief Olga Rudenko’s weekly newsletter on everything Ukraine\",\"index\":2,\"imgSrc\":\"/assets/images/kiv3/newsletters/newsletter-ukraine-weekly-small.webp\",\"mainImgSrc\":\"/assets/images/kiv3/newsletters/newsletter-ukraine-weekly-bg-4.png\",\"mainImgObjectPosition\":\"center\",\"tags\":[\"UW-newsletter-page\",\"Ukraine Weekly Newsletter\"],\"newslettersPageTags\":[\"UW-newsletter-page\",\"Ukraine Weekly Newsletter\"],\"newsletterLandingTags\":[\"UW-landing\",\"Ukraine Weekly Newsletter\"],\"newslettersBoxTags\":[\"UW-newsletters-block\",\"Ukraine Weekly Newsletter\"],\"newslettersAccountTags\":[\"UW-account-pref\",\"Ukraine Weekly Newsletter\"],\"isMain\":false,\"isDefaultSelected\":true,\"period\":\"Weekly\",\"ga\":\"uw\",\"forBox\":true,\"forSignUp\":true}},{\"id\":\"d85190a5f5\",\"name\":\"War Notes\",\"extraData\":{\"id\":\"d85190a5f5\",\"href\":\"https://us20.campaign-archive.com/?u=5ede1a4645edfb08941f4a9f9\u0026id=46160aa9be\",\"previewHref\":\"https://us20.campaign-archive.com/?u=5ede1a4645edfb08941f4a9f9\u0026id=46160aa9be\",\"link\":\"war-notes\",\"period\":\"Weekly\",\"name\":\"War Notes\",\"description\":\"\\n\\t\\t\\t\u003cp\u003eRead the second season of War Notes – a Kyiv Independent newsletter presenting you with an overview of the main developments of the war in Ukraine. This new series will be presented by the Kyiv Independent’s war reporters, and will often be coming straight from the front lines.\u003c/p\u003e\\n\\t\\t\",\"shortDescription\":\"Weekly war update by the Kyiv Independent\",\"tags\":[\"WN-landing\",\"WN-newsletter-page\",\"War Notes Newsletter\"],\"newslettersPageTags\":[\"WN-newsletter-page\",\"War Notes Newsletter\"],\"newsletterLandingTags\":[\"WN-landing\",\"War Notes Newsletter\"],\"newslettersBoxTags\":[\"WN-newsletters-block\",\"War Notes Newsletter\"],\"newslettersAccountTags\":[\"WN-account-pref\",\"War Notes Newsletter\"],\"index\":3,\"imgSrc\":\"/assets/images/kiv3/newsletters/newsletter-war-notes.webp\",\"mainImgSrc\":\"/assets/images/kiv3/newsletters/newsletter-war-notes-img.png\",\"mainImgObjectPosition\":\"center\",\"isMain\":false,\"isDefaultSelected\":false,\"ga\":\"wn\",\"forBox\":true,\"forSignUp\":true}},{\"id\":\"a0b336178f\",\"name\":\"WTF is wrong with Russia?\",\"extraData\":{\"id\":\"a0b336178f\",\"href\":\"https://us20.campaign-archive.com/?u=5ede1a4645edfb08941f4a9f9\u0026id=d523bee2d8\",\"previewHref\":\"https://us20.campaign-archive.com/?u=5ede1a4645edfb08941f4a9f9\u0026id=e6cf424b63\",\"link\":\"wtf-is-wrong-with-russia\",\"name\":\"WTF is wrong with Russia?\",\"description\":\"\\n\\t\\t\\t\u003cp\u003eThe Kyiv Independent is launching a newsletter focusing on Russia, its politics, history, and culture – all of which influence the country's brutal all-out war against Ukraine.\u003c/p\u003e\\n\\t\\t\\t\u003cp\u003eEvery Thursday, the Kyiv Independent will update you on the main news from Vladimir Putin's Russia with an analysis on current events and their wider political and historical context.\u003c/p\u003e\\n\\t\\t\",\"shortDescription\":\"A weekly newsletter about Russian politics, history, and culture, and why it’s not as mysterious as some would think\",\"index\":4,\"imgSrc\":\"/assets/images/kiv3/newsletters/wtfr-small-img.jpg\",\"mainImgSrc\":\"/assets/images/kiv3/newsletters/wtfr-big-img.webp\",\"mainImgObjectPosition\":\"center\",\"tags\":[\"WTFR-newsletter-page\",\"WTFR Newsletter\"],\"newslettersPageTags\":[\"WTFR-newsletter-page\",\"WTFR Newsletter\"],\"newsletterLandingTags\":[\"WTFR-landing\",\"WTFR Newsletter\"],\"newslettersBoxTags\":[\"WTFR-newsletters-block\",\"WTFR Newsletter\"],\"newslettersAccountTags\":[\"WTFR-account-pref\",\"WTFR Newsletter\"],\"isMain\":false,\"isDefaultSelected\":false,\"period\":\"Weekly\",\"ga\":\"wtfr\",\"forBox\":true,\"forSignUp\":true}},{\"id\":\"2d85bfcbaa\",\"name\":\"Ukraine Business Roundup\",\"extraData\":{\"id\":\"2d85bfcbaa\",\"href\":\"https://us20.campaign-archive.com/?u=5ede1a4645edfb08941f4a9f9\u0026id=d659d95931\",\"previewHref\":\"https://us20.campaign-archive.com/?u=5ede1a4645edfb08941f4a9f9\u0026id=20c66ede91\",\"link\":\"ukraine-business-roundup\",\"period\":\"Weekly\",\"name\":\"Ukraine Business Roundup\",\"description\":\"\\n\\t\\t\\t\u003cp\u003eWant to know what’s happening in the world of business and technology in Ukraine?\u003c/p\u003e\\n\\t\\t\\t\u003cp\u003eSubscribe to the Kyiv Independent’s Ukraine Business Roundup.\u003c/p\u003e\\n\\t\\t\\t\u003cp\u003eEach week, our business editor will select the biggest stories of the week in business and send them directly to your inbox.\u003c/p\u003e\\n\\t\\t\",\"shortDescription\":\"A weekly newsletter with the top business news from Ukraine\",\"tags\":[\"UBR-landing\",\"BD-newsletter-page\",\"Ukraine Business Roundup Newsletter\"],\"newslettersPageTags\":[\"UBR-newsletter-page\",\"Ukraine Business Roundup Newsletter\"],\"newsletterLandingTags\":[\"UBR-landing\",\"Ukraine Business Roundup Newsletter\"],\"newslettersBoxTags\":[\"UBR-newsletters-block\",\"Ukraine Business Roundup Newsletter\"],\"newslettersAccountTags\":[\"UBR-account-pref\",\"Ukraine Business Roundup Newsletter\"],\"index\":5,\"isDefaultSelected\":false,\"imgSrc\":\"/assets/images/kiv3/newsletters/newsletter-ukraine-business-small-cover.jpeg\",\"mainImgSrc\":\"/assets/images/kiv3/newsletters/newsletter-ukraine-business-big-cover-img.png\",\"mainImgObjectPosition\":\"center\",\"isMain\":false,\"ga\":\"ubr\",\"forBox\":true,\"forSignUp\":true}},{\"id\":\"fa4185abbb\",\"name\":\"Explaining Ukraine with Kate Tsurkan\",\"extraData\":{\"id\":\"fa4185abbb\",\"href\":\"https://us20.campaign-archive.com/?u=5ede1a4645edfb08941f4a9f9\u0026id=d523bee2d8\",\"previewHref\":\"https://mailchi.mp/kyivindependent/explaining-ukraine-with-kate-tsurkan?e=023e7d3f7b\",\"link\":\"explaining-ukraine\",\"name\":\"Explaining Ukraine with Kate Tsurkan\",\"description\":\"\\n\\t\\t\\t\u003cp\u003eEvery Tuesday, Kyiv Independent’s culture reporter Kate Tsurkan delves into different facets of Ukrainian culture, history, and sociopolitics to help you better understand contemporary Ukraine.\u003c/p\u003e\\n\\t\\t\",\"shortDescription\":\"A weekly newsletter exploring Ukrainian culture, history, and sociopolitics to help you better understand contemporary Ukraine\",\"index\":6,\"imgSrc\":\"/assets/images/kiv3/newsletters/explaning-ukraine-short.jpg\",\"mainImgSrc\":\"/assets/images/kiv3/newsletters/explaning-ukraine-main.jpg\",\"mainImgObjectPosition\":\"center\",\"tags\":[\"Explaining Ukraine\",\"EU-newsletter-page\"],\"newslettersPageTags\":[\"EU-newsletter-page\",\"Explaining Ukraine\"],\"newsletterLandingTags\":[\"EU-landing\",\"Explaining Ukraine\"],\"newslettersBoxTags\":[\"EU-newsletters-block\",\"Explaining Ukraine\"],\"newslettersAccountTags\":[\"EU-account-pref\",\"Explaining Ukraine\"],\"isMain\":false,\"isNew\":true,\"isDefaultSelected\":false,\"period\":\"Weekly\",\"ga\":\"eu\",\"forBox\":true,\"forSignUp\":true}},{\"id\":\"b62dc87925\",\"name\":\"Belarus Weekly\",\"extraData\":{\"id\":\"b62dc87925\",\"href\":\"https://us20.campaign-archive.com/?u=5ede1a4645edfb08941f4a9f9\u0026id=319779eec0\",\"previewHref\":\"https://us20.campaign-archive.com/?u=5ede1a4645edfb08941f4a9f9\u0026id=ec250f210d\",\"link\":\"belarus-weekly\",\"period\":\"Weekly\",\"name\":\"Belarus Weekly\",\"description\":\"\u003cp\u003eThe Kyiv Independent continues to provide readers with a weekly roundup to help explain current events in Belarus. This newsletter is written by Belarusian journalist Maria Yeryoma, and edited by Deputy Chief Editor Oleksiy Sorokin.\u003c/p\u003e\\n\u003cp\u003eYou will hear from us every Wednesday.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"shortDescription\":\"A weekly roundup explaining current events in Belarus\",\"tags\":[\"BW-landing\",\"BW-newsletter-page\",\"Belarus Weekly Newsletter\"],\"newslettersPageTags\":[\"BW-newsletter-page\",\"Belarus Weekly Newsletter\"],\"newsletterLandingTags\":[\"BW-landing\",\"Belarus Weekly Newsletter\"],\"newslettersBoxTags\":[\"BW-newsletters-block\",\"Belarus Weekly Newsletter\"],\"newslettersAccountTags\":[\"BW-account-pref\",\"Belarus Weekly Newsletter\"],\"index\":7,\"imgSrc\":\"/assets/images/kiv3/newsletters/newsletter-belarus-weekly.jpeg\",\"mainImgSrc\":\"/assets/images/kiv3/newsletters/newsletter-belarus-weekly.jpeg\",\"mainImgObjectPosition\":\"bottom\",\"isMain\":false,\"isDefaultSelected\":false,\"ga\":\"bw\",\"forBox\":true,\"forSignUp\":true}},{\"id\":\"9cdc5d98a3\",\"name\":\"One story from Ukraine\",\"extraData\":{\"id\":\"9cdc5d98a3\",\"href\":\"\",\"previewHref\":\"\",\"link\":\"one-story-from-ukraine\",\"name\":\"One story from Ukraine\",\"description\":\"\\n\\t\\t\\t\u003cp\u003eTo bring you the best of our reporting in a concise, accessible format, we've launched the One story from Ukraine newsletter. From Monday to Friday, we will be delivering one important story directly to your inbox, offering you a fresh look at the situation in and around Ukraine. The stories would range from field reports from Ukraine’s front lines to analysis of the Russian economy, from reports on Kyiv’s domestic and foreign affairs, to long reads about Ukraine’s culture and history.\u003c/p\u003e\\n\\t\\t\",\"shortDescription\":\"From Monday to Friday, we will be delivering one important story directly to your inbox, offering you a fresh look at the situation in and around Ukraine.\",\"index\":8,\"imgSrc\":\"/assets/images/kiv3/newsletters/one-story-from-ukraine-short.png\",\"mainImgSrc\":\"/assets/images/kiv3/newsletters/one-story-from-ukraine-main.png\",\"mainImgObjectPosition\":\"center\",\"tags\":[\"OSFU-newsletter-page\",\"OSFU Newsletter\"],\"newslettersPageTags\":[\"OSFU-newsletter-page\",\"OSFU Newsletter\"],\"newsletterLandingTags\":[\"OSFU-landing\",\"OSFU Newsletter\"],\"newslettersBoxTags\":[\"OSFU-newsletters-block\",\"OSFU Newsletter\"],\"newslettersAccountTags\":[\"OSFU-account-pref\",\"OSFU Newsletter\"],\"isMain\":false,\"isNew\":true,\"isDefaultSelected\":false,\"period\":\"Monday to Friday\",\"ga\":\"osfu\",\"forBox\":true,\"forSignUp\":true}}]}]\n"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,